that makes them ill

695
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:37,600
due to a conflict between reality

696
00:32:37,750 --> 00:32:38,990
and what they think

697
00:32:39,030 --> 00:32:40,310
through suggestions
by others or themselves.

698
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:41,440
Prodigies are one of a kind.

699
00:32:41,470 --> 00:32:42,470
You recite that bit so easily.

700
00:32:42,510 --> 00:32:44,270
However, that's only if they're alone.

701
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:45,750
It doesn't happen
in groups of two or three,

702
00:32:45,790 --> 00:32:47,270
let alone in over 100 people at once.

703
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:47,990
Of course it does.

704
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:51,600
It's mass hysteria.

705
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:52,360
What?

706
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:53,710
Summer of 1518.

707
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:54,880
It happened in Strasbourg.

708
00:32:54,990 --> 00:32:55,840
Out of nowhere,

709
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:56,510
