710
00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:57,270
Do you remember?

711
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:58,070
No.

712
00:32:58,510 --> 00:32:59,640
A woman started to dance

713
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,160
down the street.

714
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:01,360
After four days of dancing,

715
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:02,200
the number of people dancing

716
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:03,270
reached 30 to 40.

717
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,640
Within a month,

718
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,550
over 400 in the city

719
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:06,310
had started dancing.

720
00:33:06,510 --> 00:33:08,030
The entire city was congested.

721
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,470
It sounds fake.

722
00:33:09,750 --> 00:33:10,640
It's not fake.

723
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:12,200
Mass hysteria

724
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,230
mainly happens in schools and factories,

725
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:13,990
places with strict rules

726
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,270
and high stress.

727
00:33:15,750 --> 00:33:16,710
Have you watched Forrest Gump before?

728
00:33:16,840 --> 00:33:17,230
I have.

729
00:33:17,750 --> 00:33:18,790
Many people started running

730
00:33:18,790 --> 00:33:19,360
alongside Forrest.

731
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:20,600
Don't you find that strange?

732
00:33:20,750 --> 00:33:22,310
That was an artistic expression.

733
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,270
I don't think so.

734
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:24,510
Sometimes,

735
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:25,600
a powerful psychological suggestion

736
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:27,030
and certain factors

737
00:33:27,270 --> 00:33:28,600
could lead to strange situations.

738
00:33:29,070 --> 00:33:29,600
For example?

739
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:30,750
An animation.

740
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:31,840
You watch animated shows?

741
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:32,840
Animation?

742
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:33,920
At 6:30 PM

743
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:34,880
on 16 December

744
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,680
1997,

745
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:36,880
a lot of people

746
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:38,360
were watching the 38th episode

747
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:39,990
of the latest hit animation series.

748
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,360
The Porygon episode.

749
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:43,880
He not only remembers the name

750
00:33:44,030 --> 00:33:44,960
and which episode.

751
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:45,960
But he also knows

752
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:47,070
exactly when and what

753
00:33:47,230 --> 00:33:47,920
it was shown.

754
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:48,510
At around

755
00:33:48,510 --> 00:33:49,600
6:50 PM,

756
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:51,120
the screen turned very bright

757
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,160
from the special effects.

758
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:53,960
Then, the kids started showing symptoms

759
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,270
from difficulty breathing

760
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:56,230
to nausea and cramps

761
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:57,270
to hallucinations and more.

762
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,200
Within half an hour,

763
00:33:58,230 --> 00:33:59,550
over 600 children

764
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:00,550
were sent to the hospital for treatment.

765
00:34:00,710 --> 00:34:02,270
Back then, they were diagnosed

766
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,510
with photosensitive epilepsy.

767
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,550
The cause was the special effects

768
00:34:04,600 --> 00:34:05,310
within the show.

769
00:34:05,510 --> 00:34:05,960
That's right.

770
00:34:06,230 --> 00:34:07,030
It's because

771
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:08,760
of an animation technique known
as "paka paka".

772
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:09,510
Simply put,

773
00:34:09,590 --> 00:34:11,150
swapping repeatedly

774
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:12,510
between different colored lights

775
00:34:12,630 --> 00:34:13,550
would create a tense atmosphere.

776
00:34:13,670 --> 00:34:14,110
Just like this.

777
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:16,030
While that does not explain

778
00:34:16,190 --> 00:34:16,920
why the first batch of kids

779
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:17,920
would be affected,

780
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:18,960
since everyone was watching at home

781
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:19,760
by themselves.

782
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:20,880
But the current research

783
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:21,630
is leaning toward

784
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:23,760
an example

785
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,670
of mass hysteria.

786
00:34:30,070 --> 00:34:30,800
Listening

787
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:31,920
