805
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:57,510
I believe it's mass hysteria.

806
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,240
Argue if you disagree.

807
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:06,720
Wait.

808
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:08,470
I suddenly thought of evidence.

809
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:09,720
What evidence?

810
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:10,760
Ignore me. Go in first.

811
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:11,760
Chang Yue, come with me.

812
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:18,440
Currently,

813
00:35:18,990 --> 00:35:20,470
we have excluded food poisoning.

814
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:22,840
All that's left are infectious diseases.

815
00:35:23,150 --> 00:35:23,960
As of right now,

816
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:25,880
we've not detected any viruses.

817
00:35:30,190 --> 00:35:30,840
It's not a virus.

