I'll search this side.

838
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:14,800
You search that side.

839
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:26,840
Even now, mass hysteria

840
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,240
is an illness

841
00:36:28,470 --> 00:36:29,630
without logical explanation.

842
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:31,440
Those who research this phenomenon,

843
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:32,110
the doctors,

844
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,720
philosophers, and anthropologists,

845
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:35,320
have not been able to correctly

846
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:36,510
